  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[烧毁记忆]]></title>
    <link href="https://qiuhaidong.github.io/blog/2022/03/31/burned-all-memory/"/>
    <updated>2022-03-31T14:04:59+08:00</updated>
    <id>https://qiuhaidong.github.io/blog/2022/03/31/burned-all-memory</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>After the night I burned all memory<br/>
my dream becomes transparent<br/>
as I trashed all yesterdays<br/>
my step becomes lighter</p>

<p>有一夜我烧掉了所有的故事<br/>
从此我的梦变透明了<br/>
有个早晨我扔掉了所有的记忆<br/>
从此我的脚步就轻盈了</p>

<p>——《飞鸟集》  泰戈尔</p>
]]></content>
